name: Grand Theft Fish Food
description:
Tex's fish Armando wants to grow big and strong. Help Armando accomplish his goals by breaking into the local aquarium and feeding him, while avoiding patrolling guards.

Controls:

Move:  A-D or Arrow Keys

Jump: Space

Interact: W or Up Arrow

Drop through Platform: S or Down Arrow

Made By: Foster Turtle

Play Testers: FlyBoy, RoomateMan

Music: https://www.bensound.com/royalty-free-music
